il of Lowland Soil in Yellow River[J]. 农业科学, 2017, 07(09): 674-679. http://dx.doi.org/10.12677/HJAS.2017.79091</p></sec><sec id="s9"><title>参考文献 (References)</title></sec></body><back><ref-list><title>References</title><ref id="hanspub.23118-ref1"><label>1</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Jones, S.B., Robbins, C.W. and Hansen, C.I. (1993) Sodic Soil Reclamation Using Cottage Checse(Acid) Whey. Arid Soil Research and Rehabilitation, 7, 51-61. &lt;br&gt;https://doi.org/10.1080/15324989309381334</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23118-ref2"><label>2</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">仝少伟, 时连辉, 刘登民, 等. 不同有机堆肥对上壤性状及微生物生物量的影响[J]. 植物营养与肥料学报, 2014, 20(1): 110-117.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23118-ref3"><label>3</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">卢佳, 邹洪涛, 张玉龙, 等. 土体重构对旱田土壤微生物及养分的影响[J]. 水土保持学报, 2014, 29(4): 295-299.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23118-ref4"><label>4</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">王树林, 祁红, 王燕, 等. 耕层重构对连作棉田土壤理化形状及棉花生长发育的影响[J]. 作物学报, 2017, 43(5): 741-753.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23118-ref5"><label>5</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">黄顾林, 左文刚, 朱晓雯, 等. 不同有机物料改良新围垦滩涂土壤的效果研究[J]. 扬州大学学报, 2015, 36(2): 51-56.</mixed-citation></ref></ref-list></back></article>